GSD.description:
net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: fix possible memory leak in mtk_probe()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.6 by commit 96bde7c4f5683d8c1c809ddb781ef3fdec9b7215, it was introduced in version v5.19 by commit 804775dfc2885e93a0a4b35db1914c2cc25172b5. For more details please see the references link.
